UNITED STATES ex rel. Ivan KATNIC, Relator-Appellant, v. Rudolph REIMER, Director, etc., Respondent-Appellee. No. 364. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 26, 1939. Irving Schwab, of New York City, for appellant. Noel Hemmendinger, of New York City, for appellee.

Before SWAN, CHASE, and PATTERSON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed in open court.
